node.title: Two people dead after being hit by vehicle in Taupō
node.description: Two pedestrians have been killed by a vehicle in Taupō this afternoon.
node.content: ["Two pedestrians have been killed by a vehicle in Taup\u014d this afternoon.", "Police say they were hit by a single vehicle about 1.42pm this afternoon on Lake Terrace.", "Police are continuing to ask motorists to avoid the area.", "An investigation into the circumstances of the crash is ongoing."]
